@NateDog_LA @Advil I love this question, here’s the math.

50ft of super 8 Kodak 50D/7203 - $45
Developing - $25
Scanned 2K resolution - $40 (4K - $80)
Total = ~$110-150

50ft of film = 3.5 minutes of footage at 18fps (210 seconds, 3,780 frames-ish) 

$110 / 210 = 52¢ per second or 03¢ per frame
